{"tid":740970,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人幫襯過潤記運輸?","createTime":"2018-07-13T09:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:43:22.000Z","uid":55697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb27daa82244c317c0998c8517d6b4dbaa56c43","tid":740970,"uid":55697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"因為工作緣故 幫襯左潤記運輸幾次<br />\n呢間垃圾公司真係不得了 以後都唔會再幫襯佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開post 都係想提提大家避免貪平中伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事源個幾星期前已經搵潤記報左價 約實晒送貨送箱時間<br />\n點知送箱當日又遲 <br />\n送貨當日遲左大半個鐘 完全無電話通知 亦都無reply email 話會遲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果到我打電話搵條八婆<br />\n佢既語氣同回覆真係世界級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「星期五落雨塞車係咁架啦 今時今日係咁架啦 約左五點你唔係預我準時五點到下嘛? 」<br />\n「你宜家唔要我咪打去叫師傅cancel 囉」<br />\n「我好忙啊 唔得閒打黎講 唔得閒send email 通知」<br />\n<br />\n前提一早通知左潤記 <br />\n收方係office hour 後就可能鎖門唔比上樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時潤記啲師傅摸門釘真係多得呢啲同事唔小<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/173446_b811c8ead59e82c94b2c2bd56ceb8c1b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F173446_b811c8ead59e82c94b2c2bd56ceb8c1b.JPG&h=7d9d8975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/173244_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F173244_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=7d53288f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}